Usage: verify_data <algorithm> <key file> <signature file> <input file>

where <algorithm> depends on the signature algorithm used:
    0 for RSA1024 SHA1
    1 for RSA1024 SHA256
    2 for RSA1024 SHA512
    3 for RSA2048 SHA1
    4 for RSA2048 SHA256
    5 for RSA2048 SHA512
    6 for RSA4096 SHA1
    7 for RSA4096 SHA256
    8 for RSA4096 SHA512
    9 for RSA8192 SHA1
    10 for RSA8192 SHA256
    11 for RSA8192 SHA512

